Moral Statement

As a matter of moral principle, the Author opposes the use of this software,
or any derived work, to intentionally harm any person, whether to their body
or soul.

Such harm includes, but is not limited to:
- Physical injury or endangerment;
- Psychological, emotional, or spiritual harm;
- Actions that encourage or enable sin, oppression, or injustice.

This statement is an expression of personal and religious conviction and is
not intended to impose additional legal restrictions beyond the MIT License.
